    <tags>bginfo</tags>
    <summary>Configure BGInfo to run when user logs in</summary>
    <description>Installs a custom.bgi file and creates a shortcut in the StartUp folder so that bginfo.exe will be run on user login.
	
	#### Package Parameters
The following package parameters can be set:

 * `/RunImmediately` - run BGInfo using the custom.bgi file immediately (rather than waiting until next user login)

These parameters can be passed to the installer with the use of `--params`.
For example: `--params '"/RunImmediately"'`.
	
	</description>
    <!-- <releaseNotes>__REPLACE_OR_REMOVE__MarkDown_Okay</releaseNotes> -->
